{"tid":1758051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「從簡歷就篩掉中國人」 ​東京大學副教授挨轟 校方道歉","createTime":"2019-11-27T00:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T01:27:58.000Z","uid":28435,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"db25cd337bb90cd77af642581063f2bfd819d99a","tid":1758051,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:01:08.000Z","msg":"擔任東京大學特任副教授的企業經營者大澤昇平，日前在個人推特上發表「不在自己公司錄用中國人」、「從簡歷就篩掉中國人」等歧視中國人言論，引發批評聲浪。東京大學認為，歧視言論違反東大憲章，隨後在官網公發布致歉聲明，稱此人為「短期雇用教師」，其言論與校方無關。<br />\n<br />\n中央社引述日本朝日新聞報導，東京大學研究所情報學環（Interfaculty Initiative in Information Studies）及學際情報學府（Graduate School of Interdisciplinary Information Studies）的31歲特任副教授大澤昇平，20日推文「敝公司Daisy不會錄取中國人」、「不會面試中國人，書面審查就會刷掉」、「在資本主義脈絡上，表現差的勞工被歧視也是理所當然」等言論。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，歧視言論在網上引發風波，東京大學大學院情報學環及學際情報學府對此發表聲明，大澤發文內容與學環及學府毫無關係，但由學環及學府一員發表這樣的言論，令人感到十分遺憾，也對因言論感到不快的民眾表達誠摯歉意。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，站在學環及學府立場，必須遵守東京大學憲章，絕不容許任何形式的歧視。<br />\n<br />\n大澤經營人工智慧（AI）研發公司Daisy，也在大型網路證券公司Monex Group等捐助東京大學的「資訊經濟AI解決方案」講座擔任講師。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，Monex Group在事件後也發表聲明，稱完全無法接受大澤的價值觀，非常令人遺憾，也表示將停止對東京大學的捐款。"},{"pid":"57eaa506cbabb51c161bccd61e29d4de21071c4f","tid":1758051,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omEX1tT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomEX1tT.jpg&h=57874f45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdqqVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrdqqVy.jpg&h=1739302f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83fbe361dd1ba7ab8bf87c90a861d668c21c0202","tid":1758051,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"He is right, dude."},{"pid":"24b2343c936dcf0b6ce62534ab538f79b65f3cf8","tid":1758051,"uid":123848,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"唔好明講丫嘛，傻嘅"},{"pid":"f110cf63f70cbfe174f385d2280eaeb067f8279b","tid":1758051,"uid":160592,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"錯在講出來"},{"pid":"604ace53775b884e72bbf99b619cdc05b770e964","tid":1758051,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:15:43.000Z","msg":"想知當唔當香港人係中國人"},{"pid":"56964d4e070883f32dac74e0c8eef9488f1ef4ac","tid":1758051,"uid":60655,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:16:12.000Z","msg":"正確 研究加中國人 等於幫中國研究 佢實偷既"},{"pid":"165afcf4a91badce51df13a951e8b6adfbeb8374","tid":1758051,"uid":32221,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:17:06.000Z","msg":"搵人送隻靜靜雞神獸俾佢喇"},{"pid":"db1d8d7b9863a236d3334c69680b280f8cd993d7","tid":1758051,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:17:20.000Z","msg":"做得太好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dadd5b9ab158d5926887303456be223bbecf18a","tid":1758051,"uid":100581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:18:55.000Z","msg":"日本好多公司都係咁做架啦，不過冇出聲姐。"},{"pid":"3b13cebb016b40dab3b45b26e560d709dabd4919","tid":1758051,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏唔得嘅"},{"pid":"6c32e2489cf65996dea5261bcabd1cb131f4eb77","tid":1758051,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:21:51.000Z","msg":"可能一堆共諜去見工, 所以twitter 呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bde7321f7ec0d0fbfa3db63e3d283ae40d63f66","tid":1758051,"uid":261699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f110cf63f70cbfe174f385d2280eaeb067f8279b","tid":1758051,"uid":160592,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score